  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.description1": "\u00266Discord: \u0026dhttps://discord.gg/UfVF8b2GFk&r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.description10": "\u0026b主城：El_mal（玩建造之牢E）, 300wan&r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.description11": "\u0026定AI：XVIII-ling, 氣球惡魔&r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.description12": "\u0026b定畫：merlin204, asanginxst&r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.description13": "\u0026b定美：Ao， 一隻路過之小吳，XVIII-ling\u0026r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.description14": "\u0026b及：諸位優模組、資包及光影包作者&r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.description15": "——P1nero",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.description2": "\u00266QQ交一群: \u0026d948180812&r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.description3": "謝一路同行之友！謝諸位優模組作者！此乃吾二次製合包，若君對模擬營感趣，可試吾另一合包：",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.description4": "\u0026a《SkilletMan》\u0026r！",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.description5": "遠夢之柩此名初為吾友所構，時吾等欲製一載史之模組，然因故未至終章...",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.description6": "\u00266《遠夢之柩》，意為藏美物於精巧之匣中沉睡，如吾等所降之墟然。\u0026r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.description7": "曾玩\u0026a《SkilletMan》\u0026r之友當知，吾不喜將務劇情及諸交互皆積於FTB界面中成，故於此合包，FTB務將多扮圖鑑之用，並隨世間交互漸啟，吾等劇情展及物集仍主以NPC言表。",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.description8": "吾亦不喜盲積模組，本合包主線所用之敵Boss模組皆適以史戰交互者。本合包用最新之史戰，帶君體驗全新之史戰附屬，證史戰強大之潛所在。",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.description9": "\u0026b鳴謝：&r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.subtitle": "“傳深海之中有一廢墟，守望此世”",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.task.325688042160411882.title": "本合包處試階，主城未臻，部分域未啟（實無藏寶箱！）",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.task.3257333974082388709.title": "若未見他章，往近處遊～",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.task.8806221034708452812.title": "\u00266本合包不取君一錢！僅於CurseForge平臺布，嚴禁第三方分發，任何第三方轉（包括用網盤）皆為侵權！歡迎舉報！\u0026r",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest711034741643803066.title": "作者之言",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.title": "序章",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest7487272814909384521.description1": "本合包已裝\u0026b{key.fast_tpa.category}\u0026r模組，豐多人遊驗！",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest7487272814909384521.description2": "默按\u00266[右ALT]\u0026r即可{key.fast_tpa.send}！",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest7487272814909384521.description3": "可自定義救難信文，及往援時之文",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest7487272814909384521.subtitle": "“{key.fast_tpa.category}”",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest7487272814909384521.task.5950346987720516679.title": "{key.fast_tpa.category}",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest9DE1A548EA3F9BA.description1": "&b司编程：P1nero",
  "ftbquests.chapter.xu_zhang.quest9DE1A548EA3F9BA.description10": "&b協宣片攝製：Arcadia",
